********************************************************************
******************************** AIM *******************************
********************************************************************

The aim of this project is to provide cutting edge widgets using 
LWUIT library.




********************************************************************
******************** STESP TO USE THIS WIDGET **********************
********************************************************************

1) Using '.jar'
	Download the jar file '/LwuitWidgets/dist/LwuitWidgets.jar'
	
2) Using source code
	Download the project '/LwuitWidgets' and link it with 
	your preferred IDE




********************************************************************
************************ DIRECTORY STRUCTURE ***********************
********************************************************************

- Lwuit-Widgets				- Parent directory encompassing all my widgets
        |
        |-- LwuitWidgets		- Indicator Widget Project		
        |    |
        |    |-- dist			- Deployment jar file directory
        |    |-- src			- Project source classes
        |    |-- build
        |    |-- lib
        |    |-- nbproject
        |    |-- res
        |    |-- test
        |
        |
        |-- LwuitIndicatorWidgetTest	- Indicator Widget Test Project
        |    |
        |    |-- dist			- Deployment jar file directory
        |    |-- src			- Project source classes
        |    |-- build
        |    |-- lib
        |    |-- nbproject
        |    |-- res
        |    |-- test
